# Save editor
Widget 21
Property
 Flags NoReliefString
 Position 625 50
 Size 170 35
 Type PushButton
 LocaleTitle {Save}
Main
 Case message of
  SingleClic :
  Begin
      Do {SavePreferences EDITOR "SetEnv EDITOR \\\"}$editor{\\\""}
  End
End

